Post.title: 706 | Welcome to 706 Youth Space NY
Post._content:
## ? | Who Are We?
706 706

706

706 Youth Space, originated in the center of the universe at Wudaokou, is the first youth space in China. It's trying to create a new form of physical space, and has created dozens of 706 locations in several cities across China, as well as incubated projects with partners who have potential.

Through the community-based operation model, 706 advocates a new lifestyle, a new concept of education, travel, residence and social philosophy, and allows young people to explore more possibilities of life.

## | Quick Start
**1. **706 DAO** discord | Join our **706 DAO** discord : https://discord.gg/47EknsnffS** **2.
